WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.919 --> 00:00:03.400
- I jump out of my car, and
I just had this moment where

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:06.534
I look at him and said, "You
can't make me go to Mexico."

00:00:06.534 --> 00:00:08.951
(rock music)

