presents "World of Blunder."

00:00:27.864 --> 00:00:29.126
If you've never been to the show before,

00:00:29.126 --> 00:00:30.708
this is a bunch of comics
telling fun stories

00:00:30.708 --> 00:00:33.033
about real shit that happened.

00:00:33.033 --> 00:00:34.169
Give it up for a very funny man,

00:00:34.169 --> 00:00:37.722
Mr. Trevor Moore
everybody, let him hear it.

